            <div type="translation">
                <p>of Mac-Coirpri son of Tan...? of Nad-S...? son of the descendant of ... </p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary"> 
               <p><q>The first name is probably Mac-Coirpri but the remainder is doubtful. As the gen. NETAS is not attested the S following NeTa probably belongs to the following word</q> (McManus 1991, 76). </p>
